function get-SQLtablecontent {
     <#   
    .SYNOPSIS   
    Function to get all content from a SQLtable
        
    .DESCRIPTION 
    Function to get all content from a SQLtable, outputs a datatable

    .NOTES	
        Author: Robin Verhoeven
